'''碘化镧'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为LaI<sub>3</sub>。

==制备==
* 碘化镧可以由单质直接化合得到：
:: <math>\mathsf{2La + 3I_2 \ \xrightarrow{\Delta}\ 2LaI_3 }</math>

* 也可由氧化镧和碘化铵加热反应得到：<ref>{{cite journal | last=Young | first=Ralph C. | last2=Hastings | first2=Jane L. | title=Reaction of Lanthanum Oxide with Ammonium Iodide | journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society | publisher=American Chemical Society (ACS) | volume=59 | issue=4 | year=1937 | issn=0002-7863 | doi=10.1021/ja01283a510 | pages=765–766}}</ref>
:: <math>\mathsf{La_2O_3 + 6NH_4I \ \xrightarrow{350^oC}\ 2LaI_3 + 6NH_3 + 3H_2O }</math>

==反应==
碘化镧、[[磷酸镧|磷酸镧]]和[[二氧化硅|二氧化硅]]在800℃下反应，生成[[三碘化磷|三碘化磷]]：<ref>{{cite journal | last=Haschke | first=John M. | title=Reactions of strontium, lanthanum, and europium iodides. Direct preparation of phosphorus triiodide from phosphates | journal=Inorganic Chemistry | publisher=American Chemical Society (ACS) | volume=15 | issue=3 | date=1976-03-01 | issn=0020-1669 | doi=10.1021/ic50157a003 | pages=508–511}}</ref>
:5 LaI<sub>3</sub> + 3 LaPO<sub>4</sub> + 8 SiO<sub>2</sub> → 3 PI<sub>3</sub> + 3 I<sub>2</sub> + 4 La<sub>2</sub>Si<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub>

用[[THF|THF]][[萃取|萃取]]LaI<sub>3</sub>可以得到无色的LaI<sub>3</sub>(THF)<sub>4</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal | last=Izod | first=Keith | last2=Liddle | first2=Stephen T. | last3=Clegg | first3=William | title=A Convenient Route to Lanthanide Triiodide THF Solvates. Crystal Structures of LnI3(THF)4 [Ln = Pr] and LnI3(THF)3.5 [Ln = Nd, Gd, Y] | journal=Inorganic Chemistry | publisher=American Chemical Society (ACS) | volume=43 | issue=1 | date=2003-12-09 | issn=0020-1669 | doi=10.1021/ic034851u | pages=214–218}}</ref>

